This paper deals with the problem of automatic detection of fake news, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the limitations of existing approaches for fake news detection, which could be relevant to the sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
